    continuous.rda

    continuous.Rd

    A data set containing continuous items information. Example data regenerated from CTA1

    continuous

    Format

    A data frame with variables:

    schid

    School ID

    id

    Student ID

    sex

    0 = boys; 1 = girls

    race

    0 = White; 1 = Others

    pretest

    Pre test scores

    stdscore

    Standardized scores

    stdscore

    Standardized scores

    trt

    Treatment assignment; 0 = control, 1 = treatment

    Y

    Outcome

    q1-q20

    20 continuous items

    Source

    CTA1

    Examples
